{
  "stem": "11274.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So usually the little children, either a boy or a girl-- we didn't have boys, so the girls were doing-- a plate with your own a home-baked cookies and covered with a nice doily, and you were bringing it to all the people, wherever Mom decided to go to bring it.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they, they gave the children some money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So you ended up with a pocket full of money after, [LAUGHS] after this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Mom baked the cookies for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And every family to other families, so they had a lot of cookies from everybody else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they had, for months probably, cookies there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what else did we do for fun?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I said, walking, mountain climbing, and some of them that knew how, they were going swimming, too, mostly the boys.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was a swimming pool in that little town nearby that there was mixed swimming.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I wasn't allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I don't know how to swim to this day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we [? didn't-- ?] Hasidic Jews, the children, the girls weren't allowed in mixed swimming pools, so we didn't learn to swim.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the boys could swim at all time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And fishing, that's right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, I forgot about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of the boys were fishing for the Shabbos for fish to have on Friday night to have the fish and to have it for the Sabbat.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there wasn't always enough money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are not always had the chance to go to another town five kilometers from our-- seven kilometers, five miles, approximately between four and five miles to a town to buy the fish.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were all fishing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The boys were fishing to have-- and we didn't have any boys.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
